name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Jeffrey ANDERSON, Petitioner

parties: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Jeffrey ANDERSON, Petitioner.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 30th day of August, 2012, the Petition for Leave to File Petition for Allowance of Appeal Nunc Pro Tunc is GRANTED. Counsel is directed to file a Petition for Allowance of Appeal within 15 days of this order.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
